- **Early Humans**:
  - *Sahelanthropus tchadensis*: ~7 million years ago (oldest known).
  - *Ardipithecus ramidus*: ~4.4 million years ago.
  - *Australopithecus afarensis* ("Lucy"): ~3.2 million years ago, bipedal.
  - *Homo habilis*: ~2.4-1.8 million years ago, used stone tools.
  - *Homo erectus*: ~1.8 million years ago, migrated out of Africa, used fire.
  - *Homo neanderthalensis*: ~150,000-30,000 years ago, robust, cold-adapted.
  - *Homo sapiens*: Arose in Africa ~200,000 years ago.

